edback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104put1665703252802.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/put1665703252802.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/put1665703252802.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"put1665703252802\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Set the number of comment lines Uniface inserts in a web page generated from a server page.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"put1665703252802__topic_d143978e1_d143979e1_d143980e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"put1665703252802__p_d143981e1_d143982e1_d143983e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$HTML_GENERATION</span> { <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code> } {<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">MINIMAL</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">STANDARD</code> |\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">VERBOSE</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">}</code></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"put1665703252802__section_h1p_dgn_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d408995e74\">Values</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"put1665703252802__ul_bxn_2gn_lwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"put1665703252802__li_d50318e1_d50319e1_d50320e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">MINIMAL</code>—filters all comment lines; default. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"put1665703252802__li_d50321e1_d50322e1_d50323e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">STANDARD</code>—filters\n               Uniface-generated comments lines. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"put1665703252802__li_d50324e1_d50325e1_d50326e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">VERBOSE</code>—instructs Uniface to\n               include all comment lines in a Web page. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"put1665703252802__section_tnf_fgn_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d408995e98\">Defaults</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"put1665703252802__table_d17420e1_d17421e1_d17422e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Assignment file:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">server assignment files</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Section:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">[WEB]</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">MINIMAL</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"put1665703252802__section_yx5_hgn_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d408995e146\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"put1665703252802__p_d143993e1_d143994e1_d143995e1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$HTML_GENERATION</span> filters HTML\n            comments, allowing differing numbers of comments during deployment and development\n            phases, without recoding.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"put1665703252802__note_rrx_jgn_lwb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> Comment lines inside\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;SCRIPT&gt;&lt;/SCRIPT&gt;</code> blocks are never removed by\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$HTML_GENERATION</span>.</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"put1665703252802__p_d143996e1_d143997e1_d143998e1\">The default is <code class=\"ph codeph\">MINIMAL</code>, which is\n            applied when <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$HTML_GENERATION</span> is omitted, a value is omitted, or an\n            incorrect value is provided.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531088\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531088\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$HTML_GENERATION Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Set the number of comment lines Uniface inserts in a web page generated from a server page. $HTML_GENERATION { = } { MINIMAL | STANDARD | VERBOSE } Values MINIMAL —filters all comment lines; default. STANDARD —filters Uniface-generated comments lines. VERBOSE —instructs Uniface to include all comment lines in a Web page. Defaults Assignment file: server assignment files Section: [WEB] Default value: MINIMAL Description $HTML_GENERATION filters HTML comments, allowing differing numbers of comments during deployment and development phases, without recoding. Note: Comment lines inside <SCRIPT></SCRIPT> blocks are never removed by $HTML_GENERATION . The default is MINIMAL , which is applied when $HTML_GENERATION is omitted, a value is omitted, or an incorrect value is provided. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}